title: Kyle Kragen emerges as valued pass rusher for Cal
text:
Photo: Michael Macor, The Chronicle Cal's Kyle Kragen, 13 sacks Washington quarterback Luke FAlk, 4 in the first quarter, as the California Bears take on the Washington State Cougars at Memorial Stadium in Berkeley, Calif., on Sat. October 3, 2015. Cal's Kyle Kragen, 13 sacks Washington quarterback Luke FAlk, 4 in...
More than a decade in the NFL brought Greg Kragen a deep understanding of defensive line play. Eighteen years removed from his final professional snap, the community college assistant coach likes to pass along some of what he learned to his son.
